The preprocessing operators, JSON/NPZ codec, schema, registry, input sanitizer,
runtime pipeline, and the TabPFN translator in this library were extracted and
adapted from vldm — specifically the `vldm/preprocessing/` subsystem and
`scripts/tabpfn_translator.py`. The code was moved verbatim except for
intra-package import rewrites (`vldm.preprocessing.*` -> `sklearn_tabpfn_ext.*`)
and a single behavioral change to the codec: on-disk operator ids are written
from each operator's registered canonical id (kept as `vldm.preprocessing.*`)
rather than its Python module path, so artifacts remain interoperable with vldm.
